<p>I visited Olin in Feb &#8216;08 and also found the campus to be rather empty.  After walking around for a while I discovered that the students were all in their classrooms 40 minutes before the start of the class period.  They were busy chatting and making last minute preparations for class.  My overall impression was that the students seem serious about their work without being neurotic.</p>

